creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Christmas Short Works Collection 2014 by various authors. Read in in English, Bulgarian, French, German, Italian and Swedish by David Wales; Greg Giordano; DomBombadil; MaryAnn; Maria Kasper; Ed Humpal; J Korth; Rob Board; Son of the Exiles; Ruth Golding; Alisson Veldhuis; Algy Pug; Lucy Perry; BeniaminoMassimo; Brian Hostick; Jessica Mells; Herman Roskams; Lars Rolander; Robert G. Smith; Rapunzelina; Bev J Stevens; Phil Chenevert; Beth Thomas; Kimberly Krause; Ray Kasper; Ronelle Spiegel; arcobaleno; Olivereading; Claudia Salto; Mary Kay. This year's Christmas collection of short stories and non-fiction, a play, poems, and bible readings features readings in English, Bulgarian, French, German, Italian and Swedish. Cast list for The Christmas Dinner: Mother Goose: Bev J Stevens
Grandfather: Ray Kasper
Grandmother: Ronelle Spiegel
Father: J Korth
Mother: Maria Kasper
Walter: Beth Thomas
Gertrude: Kimberly Kraus
Santa Claus: Phil Chenevert
Narrator: MaryAnn Spiegel

Edited by: MaryAnn Spiegel For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
